@baseUrl = https://localhost:7046/api
@contentType = application/json

### Variables
@token = tu_token_aqui
@adminUserId = 1
@readerId = 2
@eventId = 1
@ticketZoneId = 1

### ==================== AUTH ====================

### Login Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "Admin123"
}

### Login Reader
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "reader@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "Reader123"
}

### ==================== EVENTS - PUBLIC ====================

### Obtener todos los eventos activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/events?onlyActive=true

### Obtener todos los eventos (incluyendo cancelados)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events?onlyActive=false

### Obtener evento por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}

### Buscar eventos con filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/search?searchTerm=concierto&location=Madrid&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10

### Buscar por rango de fechas
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/search?startDate=2026-06-01&endDate=2026-12-31

### ==================== EVENTS - ADMIN ====================

### Crear evento (solo Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Concierto de Rock",
  "description": "Un increíble concierto de rock con bandas locales",
  "eventDate": "2026-07-15T19:00:00",
  "location": "Madrid, Palacio Vistalegre",
  "createdBy": {{adminUserId}}
}

### Editar evento (solo Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Concierto de Rock - Actualizado",
  "description": "Un increíble concierto de rock con bandas locales",
  "eventDate": "2026-07-20T19:00:00",
  "location": "Madrid, Palacio Vistalegre"
}

### Cancelar evento (solo Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== TICKET ZONES ====================

### Obtener zonas de un evento
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticketzones/event/{{eventId}}

### Crear zona de tickets (solo Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ticketzones
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "eventId": {{eventId}},
  "name": "VIP",
  "price": 150.00,
  "totalCapacity": 100
}

### Crear zona General
POST {{baseUrl}}/ticketzones
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "eventId": {{eventId}},
  "name": "General",
  "price": 50.00,
  "totalCapacity": 500
}

### Editar zona de tickets (solo Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/ticketzones/{{ticketZoneId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "VIP Premium",
  "price": 200.00,
  "totalCapacity": 150
}

### ==================== TICKET PURCHASES ====================

### Comprar tickets
POST {{baseUrl}}/ticketpurchases/buy
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "eventId": {{eventId}},
  "ticketZoneId": {{ticketZoneId}},
  "userId": {{readerId}},
  "quantity": 2
}

### Obtener mis compras (usuario actual)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticketpurchases/my-purchases
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== REPORTS & DASHBOARD ====================

### Dashboard de ventas - Todos los eventos (solo Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/sales-dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dashboard de ventas - Evento específico (solo Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/sales-dashboard?eventId={{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mis tickets comprados
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/my-tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== NOTAS ====================
# - Reemplaza {{token}} con tu JWT token obtenido del login
# - Reemplaza los IDs de evento, zona, usuario según sea necesario
# - Algunos endpoints requieren autenticación (Authorization: Bearer)
# - Solo Admin puede crear/editar/cancelar eventos y zonas
# - Solo Admin puede ver el dashboard de ventas
# - Cualquier usuario autenticado puede comprar tickets
# - Cualquiera puede ver eventos públicos sin autenticación
